snippet.title: El Dorado: The Golden City Builder - Gameplay Trailer | STEAM
snippet.description:
El Dorado: The Golden City Builder on Steam! 🗿

Wishlist now to don't miss the news! ⤵️
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1451470/El_Dorado_The_Golden_City_Builder/

Strategy city-building game in which you plan, build and develop your settlement to conquer Jukatan and earn the title of The Golden City. Become a leader, whom even Gods will bow to. Offer sacrifices to the Gods to earn their favor, but beware and don’t lose yourself in your riches.
